  "description": "<p>日前英国《每日邮报》报道称，英国一名8岁的小女孩Lily在玩父亲的iPad上的免费游戏时，无意间购买内置道具、关卡等花费了4000英镑(约合人民币3.7万元)，其父亲尼尔为还债尼尔不得不卖掉他的汽车和摩托车以偿还债务。<strong>起先，尼尔向苹果公司申请撤销这笔款项，他认为一个小女孩在对金钱没有任何概念的情况下做出的买卖是可以忽略的，但苹果公司拒绝了这一请求。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef2cdba/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245450.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%80%E5%9B%9E8%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5iPad%E4%B8%8A%E2%80%9C%E5%9D%91%E7%88%B9%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%844000%E8%8B%B1%E9%95%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245450.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%80%E5%9B%9E8%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5iPad%E4%B8%8A%E2%80%9C%E5%9D%91%E7%88%B9%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%844000%E8%8B%B1%E9%95%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245450.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%80%E5%9B%9E8%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5iPad%E4%B8%8A%E2%80%9C%E5%9D%91%E7%88%B9%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%844000%E8%8B%B1%E9%95%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245450.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%80%E5%9B%9E8%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5iPad%E4%B8%8A%E2%80%9C%E5%9D%91%E7%88%B9%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%844000%E8%8B%B1%E9%95%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245450.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E9%